            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">46.202-3</ph> Standard inspection requirements.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d2655e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2669e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Standard inspection requirements are contained in the clauses prescribed in <xref href="FAR-i1072249.dita#i1072249"
                        base="i1072249"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">46.302</xref> through <xref href="FAR-i1072292.dita#i1072292"
                        base="i1072292"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">46.308</xref>, and in the product and service specifications that are included in solicitations and contracts.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2669e32" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The clauses referred to in (a) of this section-</p>
					          <ol id="d2655e38" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2669e42" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Require the contractor to provide and maintain an inspection system that is acceptable to the Government;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2669e51" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Give the Government the right to make inspections and tests while work is in process; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2669e60" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Require the contractor to keep complete, and make available to the Government, records of its inspection work.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
		    </conbody>
